snippet.title: Palworld | FEYBREAK Update Trailer | Palnews | Pocketpair | The Game Awards 2024
snippet.description:
🚨Palworld: Feybreak releases on Dec. 23!🚨
New Pals!✨
New Weapons!🔫
New Buildings!🔨
New Mechanics!🤖
A new Faction Leader!⚠️

A new island six times bigger than last update's Sakurajima!!!
Plus, don't miss the #Palworld 25% off Steam sale!💰

✨Available now on the PlayStation Store✨
＜PSStore URL＞
https://store.playstation.com/product/UP6360-PPSA23126_00-0112788005082769

🔥Available Now🔥
#Palworld, an open-world survival crafting game.

👇Palworld's Available on STEAM
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1623730/?utm_source=youtube&utm_medium=social-media&utm_campaign=20230304-default&utm_content=en
